description: Dominic Lazarus stands down after being removed from the same post in Guernsey for "incompetence".
title: Jersey's civil aviation director resigns following 'incompetence' report
title_page: Jersey's civil aviation director resigns following 'incompetence' report - BBC News
maintext: The Government of Jersey said it was "committed" to keeping the position as a joint Channel Islands role, and said it would be working with Guernsey colleagues "over the next few months to progress this".
